\v 39 Jaain²¹ 'in tsá² røøi²¹ tsaa² 'in táain² co' do gasɨɨ'²¹ɨ Jesús jin'²in: 
\p ―Wana 'nʉ Cristo laai²¹² 'wo'o joongɨ laai²¹² jna'a. 
